            <p>
  How to Resize the Image?<br />
  First upload the image and click on resize button(left side panel) then image will be resized and click on download button(right side top corner)
  </p>
   <p>
How to crop the image?<br />
First upload the image and select the portion of image that you want to crop. and click on crop image button(left side of panel)
</p>
<p>
How to Apply Black and White to Image?<br />
Upload the image and check the Apply B&W (in left side of the panel).
</p>
<p>
 How to rotate image in clockwise and anticlockwise direction ?<br />
Upload the image and click on left arrow(right side top corner) for clock wise direction and anticlock wise direction click on right arrow.<br />
for each click it rotates 90 degrees
</p>
<p>
How to send the Email?
<br />
Enter the email id in textbox(top right corner) and click on email button mail will be send to corresponding mail id with attached image.
</p>
